snippet.title: SRB2 Heroes with TEAMS (Download)
snippet.description:
New version of my Heroes mod (and most likely final). Some bug fixes, graphic updates, all 4 teams added, and 34 emblems to find!

- Custom Action 1 is for Lightdash.
- Custom Action 2 and 3 are for changing characters.

Please ignore the bad quality of the video, I had a LOT of problems recording it :(

You can download the mod HERE: http://mb.srb2.org/showthread.php?t=40876
